# Fast local safety net. Order is cheapest-first so you see failures
# quickly: auto-fix + lint on staged files, then whole-project typecheck,
# then the mocked test suite (no network, runs in ~300ms).
# Live tests are NOT run here -- they need credentials and cost LLM tokens.
# If you really need to bypass (e.g. WIP branch, known broken), use:
#   git commit --no-verify
npx lint-staged
npm run typecheck
npm test
